Template: simple-waf/hostname
Type: string
Default: 127.0.0.1:80
Description: Site hostname and port
 Input hostname or IP, please

Template: simple-waf/port
Type: string
Default: 80
Description: Waf listen port
 Input port for WAF, please

Template: simple-waf/pass
Type: password
Description: root user password
 Input root password for waf-admin http://localhost:8000

Template: simple-waf/https
Type: boolean
Description: Generate self-signed certs 
 Enable https
